- fix debug console in web UI
- finish tvDB support (commented out as of initial cloning)
- add Clear Completed Seeding (Downloaded and Seed Ratio Met) to Torrent config panel and rss_dl.php (keeps Transmission clean after seeding complete)
- add toggle to config for local/remote Transmission and disable features like Deep Directories and Watch Directory for remote Transmission

